Intruducion:

This project is used to do rule_classification

predict.py is the main file of project, It will read the rule file in the rule.txt, Also use the washing_function in clean.py.

clean.py support the wash_function.

rule.txt define the rule what you need and set the threshold, if result > threshold, the class label is 1, else is 0. Please follow the format. you can not only change the rule_content, but also change the weight for each rule and threshold.


Usage:
python predict.py


Requirement:
python 2.7
